folder: St. Nicholas Avenue & 153rd Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
St. Nicholas Avenue, at the northeast corner of West 153rd St., showing an old frame mansion.

E. P. Chrystie

folder: St. Nicholas Avenue & 153rd Street (West), Manhattan, NY
text:
882-888 St. Nicholas Ave., east side, between West 153rd and 155th Streets, and facing West 154th Street. These buildings are frame houses, and are set back from the building line, with their fronts obstructed by a fence.

August 29, 1935.

P. L. Sperr.
